  <summary date="2020-12-17T19:35:37Z" status="Introduced in House">Comprehensive Review of Military Suicide Act

This bill requires the Department of Defense to issue and implement guidance that requires that each suicide involving a member of the Armed Forces be reviewed by a multidisciplinary board established at the command or installation level.</summary>
